{"tid":2337902,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"鄺頌晴: 德國聽證會將於1月25日舉行 預料港府將會通緝她","createTime":"2020-12-23T15:29:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T02:45:31.000Z","uid":240362,"like":548,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":104,"replies":[{"pid":"2479aa7ead2d54db63ae33e2ac8e780b878d789d","tid":2337902,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T15:29:39.000Z","msg":"今年10月成功與被中國驅逐出境的德籍清華大學學生穆達偉（David Missal）收集5萬個聯署，促成德國國會就香港局勢舉行聽證會的「滑鼠娘娘」、前「鍵盤戰線」發言人鄺頌晴今宣佈，德國聽證會將於來年1月25日舉行，她屆時會作供，並預料港府將會通緝她。<br />\n<br />\n將就香港政治形勢作供 憂黎智英被送中受審<br />\n<br />\n鄺表示，聽證會上，將會有德國的外交官員出席並接受議員質詢，由於來年是德國選舉年，希望聽證會能成為不同候選人作出政治承諾以及宣示其對華政策的平台。她續表示，她與穆達偉屆時會就香港過去一年的事件作供，包括「12港人」、滙豐先後凍結流亡海外的前立法會議員許智峯及北區好鄰舍教會戶口、少年政治犯囚權問題、傳媒自由被收窄，以及香港過去一年的教育風波等，「其實我喺聽證會要講嘅就係香港收咗皮㗎喇」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201223/VYGYL6B7XNCPDCM4UOVKUQ2JZU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201223%2FVYGYL6B7XNCPDCM4UOVKUQ2JZU%2F&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVpx3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=f1f80d21\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201223%2FVYGYL6B7XNCPDCM4UOVKUQ2JZU%2F&h=36ba330a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201223/VYGYL6B7XNCPDCM4UOVKUQ2JZU/</a>"},{"pid":"15c96b74e94050015d65dd6b9ded1595aa708815","tid":2337902,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T15:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"925cb909acf650031810eb56eb28e7c8544071a7","tid":2337902,"uid":79117,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34